[34m│[0m | $ne      | not equal          | Bypass auth with "not admin"  |            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | $gt      | greater than       | Match values above threshold  |            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | $lt      | less than          | Match values below threshold  |            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | $regex   | regular expression | Pattern-based extraction      |            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | $nin     | not in array       | Exclude specific values       |            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | $in      | in array           | Match multiple values         |            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | $exists  | field exists       | Check for field presence      |            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | $where   | JavaScript eval    | Complex conditions (dangerous)|            [34m│[0m
